How to Delete Your Data from 23andMe:

1. Log into your 23andMe Data account.
2. ⁠Go to “Settings”.
3. ⁠Scroll down to “23andMe Data” at the bottom of the page.
4. ⁠Click “View” next to “23andMe Data”.
5. ⁠Download your data and store it securely on your device.
6. ⁠Scroll to the “Delete Data” section.
7. ⁠Click “Permanently Delete Data”.
8. ⁠Confirm your request: you will receive and email from 23andMe. Follow the link in the email to confirm your deletion request.
